{
  "stem": "12052.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what they did-- what they didn't want the production for the Germans to have iron-- so what they did-- they brought cooler iron into the-- to the rolling mills, and they told us, put full steam.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where they-- where they put the higher RPMs on the machine.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And here, they put the-- the iron in, and here there was an explosion.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, between the steam engine and the rolling mills is a big coupling, what is like, I don't know, like-- like this table or several chairs.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they just tore it apart.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They simmered down, and for several days, we-- the production had to stop.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that was a big disadvantage for the Germans, where the iron was very essential for their economy.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And when the front [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] advanced, we-- we had some news this-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] this-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we'd be evacuated.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So one fellow particularly, who I was befriended from Polish people, he says--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] His name was Vladek Pavelec.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a slim, tall guy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he got to like me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he says-- in Polish, he says, why don't you come with me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Tell your father.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Last day.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He told me where he will wait for me and we will escape.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I told my father, and my father, he says, you know, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What-- while-- if the front comes back, they catch you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if they catch him, they would kill him, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so there was a big-- but he-- he was ready to-- to-- to risk his life and take us, only my father somehow didn't-- didn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then later on, we were gathered.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
